，用心服务”为核心价值，一切以用户需求为中心，通过技术壁垒、专业水平和不懈努力，重塑国产数据库形象，为国产数据库、大数据、人工智能和区块链相关领域提供高品质产品。</p>\";s:15:\"company_img_eng\";s:81:\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/gy.png\";s:16:\"company_cont_eng\";s:1164:\"In 2008, based on the ideal of developing domestic high-performance data security system, the R &amp; D team of founding branch started the research and development of data security and database system. Several scientific research companies were successively established and finally determined to launch products and services under the brand of Huateng. Huateng digital cloud (Beijing) Technology Co., Ltd. was founded in 2016 with a registered capital of 10 million yuan. It is a domestic data company with high-performance security Database, security big data core technology and national nuclear high-tech professional product R &amp; D company.\r\n\r\nBased on ten years of research and development, Huateng is determined to become an outstanding domestic database series products and big data service provider.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWith the core value of \"focusing on technology and attentive service\", Huateng focuses on user demand, reshapes the image of domestic databases through technical barriers, professional level and unremitting efforts, and provides high-quality products for domestic databases, big data, artificial intelligence and blockchain related fields.\";}','yes'),(257,'polylang','a:15:{s:7:\"browser\";b:1;s:7:\"rewrite\";i:1;s:12:\"hide_default\";i:1;s:10:\"force_lang\";i:1;s:13:\"redirect_lang\";i:0;s:13:\"media_support\";i:1;s:9:\"uninstall\";i:0;s:4:\"sync\";a:0:{}s:10:\"post_types\";a:0:{}s:10:\"taxonomies\";a:0:{}s:7:\"domains\";a:0:{}s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"2.6.2\";s:16:\"first_activation\";i:1575941793;s:12:\"default_lang\";s:2:\"zh\";s:9:\"nav_menus\";a:1:{s:7:\"huateng\";a:2:{s:11:\"header-menu\";a:2:{s:2:\"zh\";i:0;s:2:\"en\";i:0;}s:7:\"sj-menu\";a:2:{s:2:\"zh\";i:0;s:2:\"en\";i:0;}}}}','yes'),(258,'polylang_wpml_s