%。\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"anquan-v3\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"anquan-v3-fl\">\n<h4>安全卫士产品特点及功能模块</h4>\n1. 支持多种<span>加密算法（含国密）</span>，可无缝对接新算法。\n\n2. 秘钥管理模块，保障系统<span>密钥安全</span>。\n\n3. 限制DBA和特权用户访问业务数据, 对业务数据进行<span>隔离保护</span>。\n\n4. 全程<span>密文移动</span>，保证数据在使用过程中不泄露。\n\n5. 对数据库内外部违规访问进行全方位<span>主动防御</span>。\n\n6. 对数据库访问<span>行为审计</span>，包括特权人员登录数据库主机的访问。\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"anquan-v3-fr\"><img src=\"http://localhost/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/ht06.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"380\" height=\"331\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-113\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>','数据库安全卫士','','inherit','closed','closed','','71-revision-v1','','','2019-12-09 14:49:46','2019-12-09 06:49:46','',71,'http://localhost/huateng/2019/12/09/71-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(116,1,'2019-12-09 14:51:20','2019-12-09 06:51:20','','ht07','','inherit','open','closed','','ht07','','','2019-12-09 14:51:20','2019-12-09 06:51:20','',73,'http://localhost/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/ht07.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(117,1,'2019-12-09 14:51:25','2019-12-09 06:51:25','<div class=\"shujuku-v1\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"shujuku-title\"><span>BIG DATA MANAGEMENT PLATFORM</span>\n<h3>大数据管理平台</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"guanli-box\">\n\n<span>中国首创大数据平台 ：</span>同时支持OLTP/OLAP的RDBMS/Hadoop/Spark大数据平台，\n支持SQL/JDBC/ODBC访问，性能比同类Hadoop/Spark提升10-30倍\n\n<span>弹性展性及高集成性 ：</span>适用当今各种主流应用场景： 5G应用、物联网、数据中心、云中心……\n\n<span>高安全保障 ：</span>内核级防泄露引擎，支持国密加密算法，避免Hadoop/Spark环境下大数据裸奔\n<div class=\"img-box\"><img src=\"http://localhost/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/ht07.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"698\" height=\"281\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-116\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','大数据管理平台','','inherit','closed','closed','','73-revision-v1','','','2019-12-09 14:51:25','2019-12-09 06:51:25','',73,'http://localhost/huateng/2019/12/09/73-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(118,1,'2019-12-09 14:53:14','2019-12-09 06:53:14','<div class=\"shujuku-v1\