stem\n\n2. Embedded database kernel level security leak engine, natural leak protection\n\n3. Adopt self-developed high-performance mass storage technology and self-developed domestic big data platform, with a performance increase of 10-30 times over the same period last year\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"img-box\"><img src=\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/cp02.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"530\" height=\"302\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-84\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shujuku-v3\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"shujuku-03-box clearfix\">\n<div class=\"txt-box\">\n<h4>Advantages of Huateng database products</h4>\nHuateng database is a comprehensive and hybrid new database management system, which adopts elastic plug-in bus storage architecture.\n\nIntegration of OLTP, OLAP, sequential storage engine, spatial data storage engine, graphics data storage engine, integrated hot, warm and cold three-tier data architecture storage engine.\n\nAt the same time, it supports structured data (row storage, column storage), spatial multi-dimensional data (row row cross storage), unstructured data (document, graph, picture), complex graph relation data (graph data). It is a panoramic comprehensive database management system.\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"biaog-box\">\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"col\">Competitive 1 advantage</th>\n<th scope=\"col\">Huateng database</th>\n<th scope=\"col\">Other domestic databases</th>\n<th scope=\"col\">ORACLE</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">Domestic independent control</th>\n<td>Have</td>\n<td>Have</td>\n<td>Do not possess</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"tr\">\n<th scope=\"row\">Core business application</th>\n<td>Have</td>\n<td>Do not possess</td>\n<td>Have</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">High performance computing applications</th>\n<td>Have</td>\n<td>Do not possess</td>\n<td>Do not possess</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"