\"shujuku-title\"><span>HUATENG DATABASE</span>\n<h3>HUATENG DATABASE</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shujuku-v1-box clearfix\">\n<div class=\"img-box\"><img src=\"http://localhost/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/cp01.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"540\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-82\"></div>\n<div class=\"txt-box\">\n<h4>Product value of Huateng database</h4>\nHuateng database is a domestic independent controllable high-performance database, which is comparable to Oracle\'s comprehensive security database.\n\nHuateng database new database engine can be widely used in Internet of things, Internet, traditional industries related business applications. Support enterprise level and cloud data center deployment, and support flexible distributed deployment. It is suitable for all kinds of big data, massive high concurrent data and other mainstream application scenarios.\n\nHuateng database has the ability to replace the existing Oracle and MySQL database systems, which can be widely used in business systems and analysis systems of military, aerospace, government, enterprises and institutions.\n\nHuateng database security suite, in the core of Huateng database, is embedded with a variety of encryption algorithms (supporting national encryption algorithm) and core technologies with technical barriers to ensure the safe access of sensitive data after encryption. It is a database system which can guarantee the access performance of sensitive data after encryption..\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shujuku-v2\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"txt-box\">\n<h4>华腾数据库特色</h4>\n完全自主知识产权, 具备三个核心技术能力：\n\n1. 性能优越的高端国产数据库，定位于高端核心业务系统\n\n2. 内嵌数据库内核级安全防泄露引擎，天然的防泄露保护\n\n3. 采用自主高性能海量列存技术 ，自研国产大数据平台，性能同比提升10-30倍\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"img-box\"><img src=\"http://localhost/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/cp02.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"530\" height=\"302\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-84\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shujuku-v3\">\n<di