existing Oracle and MySQL database systems, which can be widely used in business systems and analysis systems of military, aerospace, government, enterprises and institutions.\n\nHuateng database security suite, in the core of Huateng database, is embedded with a variety of encryption algorithms (supporting national encryption algorithm) and core technologies with technical barriers to ensure the safe access of sensitive data after encryption. It is a database system which can guarantee the access performance of sensitive data after encryption..\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shujuku-v2\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"txt-box\">\n<h4>Features of Huateng database</h4>\nFully independent intellectual property with three core technical capabilities：\n\n1. High end domestic database with superior performance, positioned in high-end core business system\n\n2. Embedded database kernel level security leak engine, natural leak protection\n\n3. Adopt self-developed high-performance mass storage technology and self-developed domestic big data platform, with a performance increase of 10-30 times over the same period last year\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"img-box\"><img src=\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/cp02.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"530\" height=\"302\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-84\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shujuku-v3\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"shujuku-03-box clearfix\">\n<div class=\"txt-box\">\n<h4>Advantages of Huateng database products</h4>\nHuateng database is a comprehensive and hybrid new database management system, which adopts elastic plug-in bus storage architecture.\n\nIntegration of OLTP, OLAP, sequential storage engine, spatial data storage engine, graphics data storage engine, integrated hot, warm and cold three-tier data architecture storage engine.\n\nAt the same time, it supports structured data (row storage, column storage), spatial multi-dimensional data (row row cross storage), unstructured data (document, graph, picture), complex graph relation data (graph data). It is a panoramic comprehensive database management system.\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"biaog-box\">\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"col\">Competitive 1 advantage</th>\n<th scope=\"col\">Huateng database</th>\n<th scope=\"col\">Other domestic databases</th>\n<th scope=\"col\">ORACLE</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">Domestic independent control</th>\n<td>Have</td>\n<td>Have</td>\n<td>Do not possess</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"tr\">\n<th scope=\"row\">Core business application</th>\n<td>Have</td>\n<td>Do not possess</td>\n<td>Have</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">High performance computing applications</th>\n<td>Have</td>\n<td>Do not possess</td>\n<td>Do not possess</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"tr\">\n<th scope=\"row\">Real time GIS industry</th>\n<td>Have</td>\n<td>Do not possess</td>\n<td>Do not possess</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">High performance data processing scenario</th>\n<td>Have</td>\n<td>Do not possess</td>\n<td>Do not possess</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shukuku-wuk\">\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/cp03.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"28\" height=\"27\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-86\"></td>\n<td><span>Multiple engines</span></td>\n<td>It adopts elastic plug-in bus storage architecture, and integrates OLTP row storage engine, OLAP column storage engine and graphics data storage engine. Domestic independent control.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/cp03.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"28\" height=\"27\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-86\"></td>\n<td><span>High performance</span></td>\n<td>Database specific engine, providing strong performance support capability. Under the premise of billions of records with large amount of data, it provides high-performance support capability for OLTP and OLAP services.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/cp03.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"28\" height=\"27\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-86\"></td>\n<td><span>High capacity</span></td>\n<td>Provide perfect support for OLAP and graph data services with large data volume and high concurrency. Single node supports tens of terabytes of data, and cluster supports PBT level data.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/cp04.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"31\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-87\"></td>\n<td><span>High availability</span></td>\n<td>It supports ha working mode, provides high availability guarantee, and high-performance distributed mode provides redundant protection and high availability between nodes.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/cp05.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-88\"></td>\n<td><span>High expansion</span></td>\n<td>Support database cluster architecture and provide linear expansion capability.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shujuku-v4\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<h4>Huateng database product function</h4>\n1. High performance storage data bus technology realizes the coexistence of high-performance OLTP engine, high-performance OLAP engine and graphics data engine.\n\n2. Based on the support of multi engine hybrid technology, Huateng database is suitable for all kinds of application scenarios, in addition to all kinds of mainstream application scenarios, especially for multi business fusion technology, massive big data processing scenarios.\n\n3. Compatible with standard SQL interface, no difficulty for technicians to use.\n\n4. Provide complete JDBC, ODBC and ado.net support.\n\n5. Provide proprietary Huateng database management tools.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shujuku-v5\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"shujuku-v5-title\">\n<h4>Features of Huateng database products</h4>\nHUATENGBASE Using proprietary technology to provide high-performance, high security, high availability of domestic database solutions.\n\nIt perfectly solves the problems of high concurrency and stability of OLTP business that cannot be solved by domestic database, supports the mixed application of OLTP / olap-htap, and greatly improves the performance of similar foreign database products.\n\n</div>\n<ul class=\"shujuku-v5-sank row\">\n \t<li style=\"list-style-type: none\">\n<ul class=\"shujuku-v5-sank row\">\n \t<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4\">\n<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/cp06-1.png\" class=\"img-responsive\">Patent memory, row memory, column memory fusion technology and distributed shard nothing technology, realizing unique <span>High performance, high concurrency and high stability</span>OLTP/OLAP transaction processing technology，The basic conditions to replace the core business system of foreign database.\n\n</div></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"shujuku-v5-sank row\">\n \t<li style=\"list-style-type: none\">\n<ul class=\"shujuku-v5-sank row\">\n \t<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4\">\n<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/cp07.png\" class=\"img-responsive\">The proprietary database kernel level data anti disclosure technology integrates transparent data encryption and decryption technology to create<span>China\'s safest database</span>\n\n</div></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"shujuku-v5-sank row\">\n \t<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4\">\n<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/cp08.png\" class=\"img-responsive\">Support distributed real-time redundant replication technology and high availability cluster technology to realize huatengbase<span>High availability and high scalability.</span>\n\n</div></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>','Huateng database','Huatengbase uses proprietary patent technology to provide domestic database solutions with high performance, high security and high availability.','inherit','closed','closed','','257-revision-v1','','','2019-12-10 16:34:20','2019-12-10 08:34:20','',257,'http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/2019/12/257-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(453,1,'2019-12-10 16:34:57','2019-12-10 08:34:57','<div class=\"shujuku-v1\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"shujuku-title\"><span>BIG DATA MANAGEMENT PLATFORM</span>\n<h3>BIG DATA MANAGEMENT PLATFORM</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"guanli-box\">\n\n<span>China\'s first big data platform ：Support at the same time&nbsp;</span>OLTP/OLAP RDBMS/Hadoop/Spark Big data platform，\nSupport SQL/JDBC/ODBC Visit，10-30 times better performance than similar Hadoop / spark\n\nFlexibility and high integration: applicable to various mainstream application scenarios today: 5g application, Internet of things, data center, cloud Center\n\nHigh security: kernel level anti disclosure engine, support national encryption algorithm, avoid big data streaking in Hadoop / spark environment\n<div class=\"img-box\"><img src=\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/ht07.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"698\" height=\"281\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-116\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','BIG DATA MANAGEMENT PLATFORM','At the same time, support RDBMS / Hadoop / spark big data platform of OLTP / OLAP, support SQL / JDBC, support SQL / JDBC, support SQL / JDBC, support SQL / JDBC, support SQL / JDBC, support SQL / JDBC, support SQL / JDBC','inherit','closed','closed','','263-revision-v1','','','2019-12-10 16:34:57','2019-12-10 08:34:57','',263,'http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/2019/12/263-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(454,1,'2019-12-10 16:35:38','2019-12-10 08:35:38','<div class=\"shujuku-v1\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"shujuku-title\"><span>ALL-IN-ONE DATABASE MACHINE</span>\n<h3>ALL-IN-ONE DATABASE MACHINE</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"yitiji-v1\">\n<div class=\"wenzi\">Huateng database integrated machine adopts general x86 server architecture, built-in Huateng distributed database storage platform and management system, Adopt the three-tier architecture of hot, warm and cold to greatly improve the data service performance.</div>\n<div class=\"clearfix\">\n<div class=\"txt-box\">\n\n1. General x86 server architecture, supporting x86 servers of current mainstream manufacturers\n\n2. Special FPGA hardware memory acceleration card adopts patent SSD and network buffer synchronization technology to break through the network and storage bottleneck\n\n3. Three layer architecture (memory, SSD, hard disk) supports three types of characteristic data: hot data, warm data and cold data\n\n4. The performance of I / O memory of special FPGA hardware memory acceleration card is improved by more than 10 times compared with that of hardware device\n\n5. Huating DBM distributed data storage platform improves data high-performance access class performance by more than 100 times\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"img-box\"><img src=\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/yiti01.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"540\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-105\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"yitiji-v2\">\n<div class=\"yitiji-v2-title\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<h4>Huateng database integrated machine product line</h4>\nHuateng database all-in-one machine is positioned in high-end business scenarios, fully realizing the value of high performance and high security.\n\nTypical application scenarios: telecommunication level application, real-time business analysis of banking and finance; real-time business analysis of large amount of industrial data; big data analysis of the Internet of things.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"yitiji-v2-sank\">\n<ul class=\"clearfix\">\n \t<li><a><img src=\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/ht01.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"196\" height=\"185\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-106\">&nbsp;<span>华腾数据库一体机</span> </a></li>\n \t<li><a><img src=\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/ht02.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"196\" height=\"185\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-107\">&nbsp;<span>华腾大数据存储一体机</span> </a></li>\n \t<li><a><img src=\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/ht03.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"196\" height=\"185\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-108\">&nbsp;<span>华腾物联大数据一体机</span> </a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','ALL-IN-ONE DATABASE MACHINE','Huateng database integrated machine adopts general x86 server architecture, built-in Huateng distributed database storage platform and management','inherit','closed','closed','','268-revision-v1','','','2019-12-10 16:35:38','2019-12-10 08:35:38','',268,'http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/2019/12/268-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(455,1,'2019-12-10 16:36:18','2019-12-10 08:36:18','<div class=\"shujuku-v1\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"shujuku-title\"><span>DATABASE SECURITY GUARD</span>\n<h3>DATABASE SECURITY GUARD</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"anquan-v1\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"anquan-v1-fl\">\n<h4>Brief introduction and working mode of security guard</h4>\nDatabase security guard is a comprehensive security protection product for structured data of Huateng digital cloud company. With transparent encryption and decryption as the core, data access control and audit as the support, the security guard has the full range of anti disclosure capabilities for enterprise data and cloud data.\n\nOne or more security guards can be deployed according to business needs. Each security guard manages one or more databases\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"anquan-v1-fr\"><img src=\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/ht04.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"541\" height=\"353\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-111\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"anquan-v2\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"anquan-v2-fl\">\n<h4>Safety guard Product advantages and value</h4>\n<div class=\"img-box\"><img src=\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/ht05.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"541\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-112\"></div>\n●Prevent the leakage of sensitive data at the root and conduct Privatization (customization) protection.\n\n●It has the ability of data protection against attack, leakage and theft in the whole life cycle of data.\n\n●Provide monitoring, early warning, control and leakage emergency response support for structured data.\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"anquan-v2-fr\">\n\n◆Huateng database security guard uses transparent agent technology to conduct security audit and firewall control on database and big data.\n\n1、审计数据库内部操作、透明加解密操作、数据库配置、SSL加密访问。\n\n2、防火墙管控SSL安全访问系统\n\n3、电信级高性能、高并发数据访问，没有漏拦截。\n\n◆支持动态加密，加密数据可逆可还原。\n\n◆基于数据库访问行为及人工智能技术实现数据库异常行为检测分析\n\n◆采用数据库透明加解密独有无损技术，透明加解密性能损失小于15%。\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"anquan-v3\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"anquan-v3-fl\">\n<h4>安全卫士产品特点及功能模块</h4>\n1. 支持多种<span>加密算法（含国密）</span>，可无缝对接新算法。\n\n2. 秘钥管理模块，保障系统<span>密钥安全</span>。\n\n3. 限制DBA和特权用户访问业务数据, 对业务数据进行<span>隔离保护</span>。\n\n4. 全程<span>密文移动</span>，保证数据在使用过程中不泄露。\n\n5. 对数据库内外部违规访问进行全方位<span>主动防御</span>。\n\n6. 对数据库访问<span>行为审计</span>，包括特权人员登录数据库主机的访问。\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"anquan-v3-fr\"><img src=\"http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/ht06.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"380\" height=\"331\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-113\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>','DATABASE SECURITY GUARD','Database security guard is a product for all-round security protection of structured data. Platform encrypting and decrypting data','inherit','closed','closed','','271-revision-v1','','','2019-12-10 16:36:18','2019-12-10 08:36:18','',271,'http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/2019/12/271-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(456,1,'2019-12-10 16:36:42','2019-12-10 08:36:42','<div class=\"guan-ban\"></div>\n<h1>正在开发中...</h1>','产品支持','','inherit','closed','closed','','212-revision-v1','','','2019-12-10 16:36:42','2019-12-10 08:36:42','',212,'http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/2019/12/212-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(457,1,'2019-12-10 16:37:08','2019-12-10 08:37:08','<div class=\"guan-ban\"></div>\n<h1>正在开发中...</h1>','技术服务','','inherit','closed','closed','','214-revision-v1','','','2019-12-10 16:37:08','2019-12-10 08:37:08','',214,'http://www.euku.net/jishuerbu/wordpress/huateng/2019/12/214-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
